rows.label: tlk45350141_09_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm afraid I don't have any
new jobs for you today.

rows.label: tlk45350141_09_msg0002
rows.name:
How about you go walk the streets,
listen to people's troubles?

rows.label: tlk45350141_09_msg0003
rows.name:
A good Driver doesn't just wait for
work to come to him, you know. He
finds what needs doing for himself.

rows.label: tlk45350141_09_msg0004
rows.name:
Though I suppose you know that
already. Sorry to be presumptuous.
